{"id":597416,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/【立此存照】妇联招聘男士优先/","date":"2018-10-11T07:46:35Z","modified":"2018-10-11T07:46:35Z","title":"【立此存照】妇联招聘“男士优先”","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>当地时间2018年10月10日，兴国县妇联官方微信公号发布招聘维权岗专职工作人员的公告，选聘条件之一赫然出现了“男性优先”。作者 @高富强 在微博对此<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/1262632003/GDkoarxz4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">进行曝光</a>后，兴国县妇联<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/n7Ymqnns2yvJqEjggYgk0A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">修改了微信原文</a>，将“男性优先”改为“男女不限”（图1）。截至发稿时，@高富强 的曝光微博已被和谐（图2）。</p>\n<blockquote><p>@高富强：大写的卧槽，兴国县妇联还有点能量，本博上一条微博阅读量超过十万加时，站方竟然限制了该条微博的转发功能。如图所示，右边的图片已经屏蔽了转发功能。什么男女平等，什么基本国策，什么舆论监督，都见鬼去吧！<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597411\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先1-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先1-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597412\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先2.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先2-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先2-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a> ​​​​</p></blockquote>\n<p><em>图1：</em></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_597414\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/-e1539238476394.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-597414\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/-e1539238476394.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"243\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">自称“妇女儿童的温暖之家”的兴国县妇联已对原招聘公告进行了修改，将“男士优先”改为“男女不限”；微信网页截图</span></p></div>\n<p><em>图2:</em></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_597413\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-597413 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先3.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/妇联-男士优先3-286x300.jpg 286w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@高富强 原微博已被删除；截图来自：新浪微博 @Naomi不高兴</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[12917,28641,26991,32558,18979,9897,11848]}